  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd3 \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0db4 \u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0d9a\u0da9\u0dcf \u0dc0\u0daf\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Patal switched cars and crashed into the petrol station",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Mirihana police say that a luxury jeep rammed into the Madiwela petrol station, seriously injuring the pump operator, while a three-wheeler and two motorbikes that came to get fuel were damaged, as well as a pump at the petrol station.",
        "The police say that while coming to the Madivela petrol station from Thalawathugoda, instead of braking, he stepped on the accelerator and rushed into the petrol station, hitting the fuel pump and overturning the pumper who was nearby.",
        "In the accident, the luxury jeep, the three wheeler, the two motorcycles, the fuel station and the pump were seriously damaged."
      ],
